td-app-finance.BERKSHIRE_DESCRIPTION: For the first time in the company’s history, Berkshire Hathaway live-streamed its annual shareholder meeting for all of the world to see. Investors and non-investors alike were able to witness history, live, as Chairman and CEO Warren Buffett and his right-hand man Charlie Munger shared their unscripted views on the company, the markets, the economy, corporate governance and even happiness. Yahoo Finance was the exclusive host of this momentous event. In case you missed it, enjoy the replay!
